{"tid":480224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浙江寧波離奇大爆炸 驚現蘑菇雲 建築物倒塌死傷嚴重","createTime":"2017-11-26T02:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T01:52:24.000Z","uid":22349,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"39964caf47063bea386b61e30673b067a792189c","tid":480224,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:41:57.000Z","msg":"浙江寧波發生爆炸事故。今天早上9時許，寧波江北區李家西路一帶突發爆炸，據現場目擊者描述情況較為嚴重，有人員傷亡。消防已經趕到現場。寧波急救中心已經調派多部救護車輪換運送傷員，並緊急調派鎮海、慈溪等地救護車輛趕來。<br />\n<br />\n網上相片所見，現場大量建築物倒塌，更有多名傷者倒臥現場，不省人事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171126&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57506311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171126%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57506311&d=r%2F49uCi42EMBuif2e4VsKJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=61c79451\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171126%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57506311&h=8053867f\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171126&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57506311</a>"},{"pid":"8a7578fe6cf3cd04f1895136572e56678af9c605","tid":480224,"uid":82532,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:43:57.000Z","msg":"沒事<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">兒</span>沒事<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">兒</span>"},{"pid":"aaf013fad5712dd35bb704aa61e54bacc55b1c40","tid":480224,"uid":15977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"還有黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b08993a0d6eb7c4ee9dd717e5848d8be3921555","tid":480224,"uid":45213,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DPZGJM5VoAA52In?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDPZGJM5VoAA52In%3Fformat%3Djpg